<section class="faq-hero text-center text-white">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Need-to-know answers</p>
    <h1>FAQ & Delivery Policies</h1>
    <p class="lead">Same-day delivery across Miami-Dade & Broward. No shipping yet—just lightning-fast couriers.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="faq-content container">
  <div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-1-h">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="faq-1">
              1. Can anyone buy from you?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq-1-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Nope—this is a 21+ experience only. Couriers and staff verify ID at pickup or delivery, so have a matching government ID ready.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-3-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-3">
              3. Where do you deliver?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-3-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              We run courier delivery across Miami, greater Miami-Dade, and Broward County. No nationwide shipping (yet).
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-4-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-4">
              4. How long till I get my order?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-4-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Most deliveries leave the shop within 60	60 minutes during business hours and arrive in 1	3 hours depending on distance and courier load.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-5-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-5">
              5. How much is delivery?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-5-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Fees are calculated at checkout based on distance and courier availability. Delivery is free once your cart hits $150+.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-6-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-6">
              6. Can I track my delivery?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-6-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Yup. Couriers send SMS/app updates as soon as theyre en route, so you can follow along in real time.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-7-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-7">
              7. What if something goes wrong?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-7-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Reach out immediately if a courier cant find you, the package looks tampered with, or anything arrives damaged. Email <a href="mailto:<%= contact.email %>"><%= contact.email %></a> or call <%= contact.phone %> within 24 hours so we can make it right.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-8-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-8">
              8. Can I return my order?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-8-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              All sales are final. If something shows up defective or DOA, let us know within 7 days with photos/video and well arrange a replacement or credit.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-9-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-9">
              9. Are there local restrictions on vaping products?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-9-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              State law requires purchasers to be 21+, and some municipalities add extra restrictions on flavored or disposable vapes. Make sure you comply with local ordinances before ordering or using any products.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq-10-h">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq-10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-10">
              10. What payment methods do you take?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="faq-10" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq-10-h" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Major cards (Visa, Mastercard, AmEx, Discover) plus Apple Pay/Google Pay. We text a secure invoice or run your card at pickup/delivery. Cash is accepted in-store with valid ID.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="faq-sidebar">
        <div class="faq-card">
          <h4>Quick links</h4>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a href="/checkout">Start checkout</a></li>
            <li><a href="/policy/delivery">Delivery policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/policy/terms">Terms of service</a></li>
            <li><a href="/policy/privacy">Privacy policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="/policy/refund">Refund policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card">
          <h4>Need help?</h4>
          <p>Email <a href="mailto:<%= contact.email %>"><%= contact.email %></a><br>Call <a href="tel:<%= contact.phone %>"><%= contact.phone %></a></p>
          <p>
            Miami Vape Smoke Shop #1<br>
            <%= contact.addresses[0] %>
          </p>
          <p>
            Miami Vape Smoke Shop #2<br>
            <%= contact.addresses[1] %>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card">
          <h4>Stay in the loop</h4>
          <p>Sign up for drops, restocks, and exclusive delivery-only bundles.</p>
          <form class="faq-form" aria-label="Newsletter signup">
            <label class="visually-hidden" for="faq-email">Email</label>
            <input id="faq-email" type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="you@email.com" required>
            <button class="btn btn-primary w-100" type="submit">Notify me</button>
          </form>
          <small class="text-muted d-block mt-2">By subscribing you confirm youre 21+ and agree to receive marketing messages.</small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
